{"tid":200064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"驚天大發現！！！終於明點解成日甩鞋帶","createTime":"2017-04-13T16:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T17:02:39.000Z","uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13391478aa0533ebf22376b9b327be72269b0bfe","tid":200064,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">放心唔係英國研究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n研究揭鞋帶鬆脫機制之謎<br />\n<br />\n鞋帶明明打好了結，為什麼總會鬆脫下來？答案原來是我們走或跑動時所產生的衝擊力和慣性拉扯力，會如同無形之手悄悄給鞋帶鬆綁。<br />\n美國加州大學柏克萊分校一組機械工程人員為了解鞋帶鬆脫的緣由，經用慢動作鏡頭拍攝研究員在跑步機上跑步期間鞋帶鬆開的過程。研究顯示，跑步時腳掌會以7倍重力擊落地面，這種瞬間衝擊力令繩結底部鬆動，到提腿前後邁步擺動時又會在鞋帶尾端衍生額外「慣性力」（inertia force），使鞋帶因慣性向外扯。這雙重作用恰似無形之手，最終令鞋帶繩結解開。研究發現，無論哪一款鞋帶和綁法，鬆脫的機制大同小異。<br />\n過往的研究大多認為，鞋帶鬆脫是因長期負荷而引致，這次則是研究動態外力在當中的角色。研究員希望，透過理解鞋帶鬆脫機制，能進一步了解DNA或一些微形結構受力下崩潰的原理。研究報告周二發表於《英國皇家學會刊》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170413/s00014/1492020191865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170413%2Fs00014%2F1492020191865&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6086ef90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170413%2Fs00014%2F1492020191865&h=c93f0023\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170413/s00014/1492020191865</a>"},{"pid":"97e67705a59313d5bd8423edf6640e18752611b7","tid":200064,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25f20eeee14c3670e5718e658546c317c4d318f8","tid":200064,"uid":55700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"樓主 我睇晒成篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b7a0426df71dde6c2c60dd8ce4b744c67709776","tid":200064,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T16:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/192370/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flihkg.na.cx%2Fthread%2F192370%2Fpage%2F1&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWXzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=429caaf6\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.na.cx/thread/192370/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ff6e879f5be91ce6e90f4526d3e0c0b6f97129cb","tid":200064,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T17:02:39.000Z","msg":"鞋帶問題<br />\n用fiction低既鞋帶咪易甩  好似 圓形 粗 硬 <br />\n<br />\n平時對鞋用 d棉 鞋帶 未甩過"}]}